org.freelte.turbodecoder

Class AlignDecoderFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.freelte.turbodecoder.AlignDecoderFrame

  • public class AlignDecoderFrame
extends java.lang.Object
    A helper to LLR demod to extract the terminating bits and packing method of LTE frame into standard logical vectors. For example, the data bits vector d0 are extended with LTE termination bits which should be unpacked and only the relevant d0 bits are attached to d0 vector.
